      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>&gt;@UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.class-features.Item.YMGOKoZtKgJqIsAD]{Mechanic Trick}</p>\n<p>You can use your knowledge of machines and technology to repair androids and robots. Whenever you attempt a Medicine check to assist an android, SRO, or other creature with the @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.Item.nyUODKP7eBP6Y6tn]{constructed} species trait or construct (technological) subtype, you can use your Engineering skill instead of Medicine to achieve the same results. Your custom rig acts as a @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.equipment.Item.4ANV2gtgo6zRffs3]{medkit} for this purpose (or an @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.equipment.Item.z95qI1bzrlZHhHQE]{advanced medkit}, if you are 5th level or higher).</p>"
